headline: D.R. Horton, Inc. to Release 2025 First Quarter Earnings on January 21, 2025
summary: ARLINGTON, Texas, December 03, 2024--D.R. Horton announced that the Company will release financial results for its first quarter ended December 31, 2024 on Tuesday, January 21, 2025.
